OL,5, The number of care workers in England  
OL,6, has fallen for the first time, leaving 
OL,7, more people without the support they   
OL,8, need, new figures reveal.              
OL,10,FUnfilled care jobs rose by 52% in a    
OL,11,Fyear, the fastest rate on record, says 
OL,12,Findustry body, Skills for Care.        
OL,14,FOne woman told the BBC the struggle to 
OL,15,Fget care for her 83-year-old mother had
OL,16,Fbeen "a nightmare".                    
OL,18,FSkills for Care Chief Executive Oonagh 
OL,19,FSmyth wants "a step change" in how we  
OL,20,Fvalue social care.                     
